			<div class="cell">
				
					Time overlaps of the Russian Stock exchange with foreign stock exchanges and their effect on liquidity: Evidence from the natural experiment
				
			</div>
			<div class="cell">
				<a href="/org/persons/244569">Гельман Сергей Викторович</a>
			</div>
			<div class="cell">
				<a href="http://icef.hse.ru/">Международный институт экономики и финансов</a>
